description: Yippee Ki Yay! First time in Trade Paperback! BOOM! Studios is proud to present America's greatest action hero translated into the sequential art form for the first time! Every great action hero got started somewhere: Batman Began. Bond had his Casino Royale. And for John McClane, more than a decade before the first DIE HARD movie, he's just another rookie cop, an East Coast guy working on earning his badge in New York City during 1976's Bicentennial celebration. Too bad for John McClane, nothing's ever that easy. Join legendary industry creator Howard Chaykin on a thrill ride that's rung up over $1 billion in box office worldwide and become the gold standard for classic action! The previously offered Hardcover edition is also offered this month!

description:
Blue Beetle is stuck in outer space, deep inside Reach Territory. That shouldnt be a problem, right? Will Jaime be pulled into the war between the Reach and...Lady Styx?!

Blue Beetle is trying to get back to earth with the help of a smuggler named Moonrunner. Moonrunner takes him to a planet that is in-between the Reach system and Lady Styx's domain. His presence become known and he become hunted by Lady Styx's men and attacked by Sky Witness who has been tracking him for a long time.
